---
// Hero.astro
---

<!-- Schema Markup for SEO -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Maitén Oviedo",
    "jobTitle": "Desarrollador Full Stack",
    "url": "https://maitendev.vercel.app/",
    "sameAs": [
      "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maiten-oviedo/",
      "https://github.com/Maiten-Oviedo",
      "https://www.instagram.com/maiten_oviedo"
    ],
    "email": "maitenoviedo513@gmail.com"
  }
</script>

<section
  class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 relative z-10 min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center"
>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 w-full mt-12 lg:mt-0"
  >
    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="flex-1 space-y-10 animate-slide-in-left">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-950/40 border border-emerald-500/10 shadow-sm"
      >
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
        <span
          class="font-label text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300/80 uppercase"
          >Disponible para nuevos desafíos</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h1
          class="text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-headline leading-[0.9] tracking-tight text-emerald-50"
        >
          Maitén <br />
          <span class="italic text-emerald-300">Oviedo</span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-emerald-100/60 max-w-xl font-body font-light leading-relaxed"
        >
          Desarrollador Full Stack. Hago aplicaciones que funcionan, duran y se
          entienden. Prefiero soluciones honestas y código legible antes que
          complicaciones innecesarias. Mendoza, Argentina.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center pt-8">
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="blob-button px-12 py-6 bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-50 font-label font-bold tracking-[0.15em] hover:bg-emerald-500/40 transition-all duration-400 active:scale-95 flex items-center gap-3 border border-emerald-500/20 shadow-organic uppercase text-sm"
        >
          Iniciar Proyecto
          <span
            class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg"
            data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="#experiencia"
          class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/50 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors border-b border-transparent hover:border-emerald-500/30 pb-1"
        >
          Ver Trayectoria
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Visual Anchor -->
    <div
      class="flex-1 relative w-full animate-fade-in-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"
    >
      <div
        class="relative w-full max-w-lg mx-auto aspect-[4/5] lg:aspect-square"
      >
        <!-- Abstract Organic Shapes -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-emerald-900/20 blur-[100px] blob-hero opacity-60"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative w-full h-full blob-hero overflow-hidden border border-emerald-500/10 shadow-2xl bg-emerald-950/20 group transition-all duration-700 hover:border-emerald-500/20"
        >
          <!-- Minimalist Glow -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="size-48 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/5 blur-[60px]">
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Abstract Background Shape -->
          <div
            class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 size-64 bg-emerald-500/5 blur-[80px] rounded-full"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Sincere Note -->
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 md:-left-12 bg-emerald-950/80 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 blob-card border border-emerald-500/10 shadow-organic max-w-[280px] z-20 animate-float-organic"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-emerald-400"
              data-icon="architecture">architecture</span
            >
            <span
              class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] text-emerald-300 uppercase"
              >Arquitectura</span
            >
          </div>
          <p
            class="text-sm font-light text-emerald-100/70 leading-relaxed font-body"
          >
            Enfoque pragmático: código fácil de mantener y con el mejor
            rendimiento posible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
